<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.9">
<l>āṅku māvali vēḷviyi lirantuceṉ ṟakaliṭa muḻutiṉaiyum</l>
<l>pāṅki ṉāṟkoṇṭa paramaniṟ paṇinteḻu vēṉeṉak karuḷpuriyē</l>
<l>yōṅku piṇṭiyiṉ cemmala rēṟivaṇ ṭuḻitara māvēṟit</l>
<l>tīṅku yilmiḻaṟ ṟumpaṭap paittiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Supreme [Lord] who took with propriety the entirety of the broad earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">having gone begging</l>
<l>There at the sacrifice of Māvali, grant grace to me who is revived</l>
<l rend="indent">worshipping you,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai with gardens</l>
<l rend="indent">where sweet[-voiced] cuckoos coo, climbing the mango trees,</l>
<l>As bees wander aimlessly, climbing [in] the red blossoms</l>
<l rend="indent">of the tall aśoka [trees].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
